item.title: Help, Shop Prices
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

The second number is the price, the numbers after the third number are the bonuses. The first and third numbers have something to do with the price, but I’m not sure what. Don’t worry about those.
